#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:vineyard.product_product_27_product_template
msgid ""
"Discover the art of Bordeaux-inspired elegance in every sip of Bordoo Grand "
"Cru. This full-bodied red boasts structured tannins and rich, age-worthy "
"depth, perfect for those who savor bold, sophisticated wines. Ideal for "
"pairing with hearty meats or enjoying slowly on its own."
msgstr ""
"ຄົ້ນພົບສິລະປະຂອງຄວາມສະຫງ່າງາມແບບ Bordeaux ໃນທຸກຢອດຂອງ Bordoo Grand Cru. ເຫຼົ້າອະງຸ່ນແດງນີ້"
"ມີແທນນິນທີ່ມີໂຄງສ້າງ ແລະ ຄວາມເຂັ້ມຂຸ້ນທີ່ເໝາະສຳລັບການບົ່ມ, ເໝາະສຳລັບຜູ້ທີ່ມັກລົດຊາດທີ່ໜັກແໜ້ນ ແລະ ຊັບຊ້ອ"
"ນ. ເໝາະສຳລັບດື່ມຄູ່ກັບຊີ້ນ ຫຼື ຊິມຢ່າງຊ້າໆດ້ວຍຕົວມັນເອງ."

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:product.template,description:vineyard.product_product_13_product_template
