msgstr "Malbec&amp;nbsp;<br/>"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage all your potential customer relationships in one place. Track "
"conversations, plan activities, and ensure timely follow-ups to secure long-"
"term contracts for distributors and restaurants."
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການສາຍສຳພັນກັບລູກຄ້າທັງໝົດໃນບ່ອນດຽວ. ຕິດຕາມການສົນທະນາ, ວາງແຜນກິດຈະກຳ, ແລະ ຮັບປະກັນການຕິດ"
"ຕາມທີ່ທັນເວລາ ເພື່ອຮັກສາສັນຍາໄລຍະຍາວກັບຕົວແທນຈຳໜ່າຍ ແລະ ຮ້ານອາຫານ."

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid "Mark it as todo to schedule it"
msgstr "ໝາຍວ່າຍັງຄົງຄ້າງ ເພື່ອວາງແຜນວຽກ"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid "May be some more tests are to be planned so you can add some from here"
msgstr "ອາດຈະມີການທົດສອບເພີ່ມເຕີມທີ່ຕ້ອງວາງແຜນ ທ່ານສາມາດເພີ່ມໄດ້ຈາກທີ່ນີ້"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Monitor and document wine quality, from grape reception to bottled product "
"release."
msgstr ""
"ຕິດຕາມ ແລະ ບັນທຶກຄຸນນະພາບຂອງເຫຼົ້າອະງຸ່ນ, ຕັ້ງແຕ່ການຮັບໝາກອະງຸ່ນຈົນເຖິງການປ່ອຍຜະລິດຕະພັນທີ່ບັນຈຸຕຸກແລ້"
"ວ."

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid "Monitor harvest performance year after year."
msgstr "ຕິດຕາມປະສິດທິພາບການເກັບກ່ຽວໃນແຕ່ລະປີ."

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo offers additional modules to further enhance your vineyard operations:"
msgstr "Odoo ມີໂມດູນເພີ່ມເຕີມເພື່ອເສີມສ້າງການດຳເນີນງານສວນອະງຸ່ນຂອງທ່ານ:"

#. module: vineyard
#: model:product.template,name:vineyard.product_product_25_product_template
msgid "Odoomatic Spice"
msgstr "Odoomatic Spice"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this package. Feel free\n"
"            to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test everything around!"
msgstr ""
"ແນ່ນອນວ່າ ນີ້ເປັນພຽງພາບລວມຂອງຄຸນສົມບັດທີ່ມີໃນແພັກເກັດນີ້. ທ່ານສາມາດ\n"
"            ເພີ່ມແອັບໃໝ່, ລຶບ/ແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງ, ແລະ ທົດລອງໃຊ້ງານທຸກຢ່າງໄດ້ຕາມໃຈ!"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Offer online booking for winery tours and tastings, with automatic "
"confirmation emails."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດໃຫ້ຈອງທົວຊົມໂຮງບົ່ມ ແລະ ຊິມເຫຼົ້າອະງຸ່ນອອນລາຍ ພ້ອມລະບົບອີເມວຢືນຢັນອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once all quality checks are completed, validate the harvest to account for "
"those grapes in your stock"
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອການກວດສອບຄຸນນະພາບທັງໝົດສຳເລັດແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ຢືນຢັນການເກັບກ່ຽວເພື່ອເພີ່ມໝາກອະງຸ່ນເຂົ້າໃນສາງຂອງທ່ານ"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once done with the field work, record the harvested quantity in the details "
