#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"With Odoo, your vineyard can reduce manual work, track performance in real "
"time, and adapt quickly to seasonal and market changes — all while "
"preserving the artistry that makes your wine unique."
msgstr ""
"ດ້ວຍ Odoo, ສວນອະງຸ່ນຂອງທ່ານສາມາດຫຼຸດຜ່ອນການເຮັດວຽກດ້ວຍມື, ຕິດຕາມຜົນງານແບບເວລາຈິງ, ແລະ ປັບຕົວ"
"ເຂົ້າກັບການປ່ຽນແປງຂອງລະດູການ ແລະ ຕະຫຼາດໄດ້ຢ່າງວ່ອງໄວ — ທັງໝົດນີ້ຍັງຄົງຮັກສາສິລະປະທີ່ເຮັດໃຫ້ເຫຼົ້າອະງຸ່ນ"
"ຂອງທ່ານໂດດເດັ່ນ."

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງການປຶກສາກ່ຽວກັບການຕັ້ງຄ່າ Odoo ກັບພວກເຮົາ ຫຼື ພັດທະນາໃຫ້ໄກກວ່ານີ້ບໍ?"

#. module: vineyard
#: model:product.template,name:vineyard.product_product_18_product_template
msgid "Yeast"
msgstr "ຢີສ (Yeast)"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard.<strong/>"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດເຂົ້າໃຊ້ທຸກແອັບທີ່ຕິດຕັ້ງໄວ້ໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນ Odoo ຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ທີ່ແດຊບອດຫຼັກ.<strong/>"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can find all quality checks performed on batches and recipe iterations "
"(ECOs) from their smart buttons."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດເບິ່ງການກວດສອບຄຸນນະພາບທັງໝົດທີ່ເຮັດກັບຊຸດການຜະລິດ ແລະ ການທົດລອງສູດ (ECOs) ໄດ້ຈາກປຸ່ມລັ"
"ດຂອງພວກມັນ."

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can mark it as failed and create a new ECO based on new learnings but "
"let's mark it as passed and come back to the test list from the breadcrumb"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດໝາຍວ່າບໍ່ຜ່ານ ແລະ ສ້າງ ECO ໃໝ່ຈາກສິ່ງທີ່ຮຽນຮູ້, ແຕ່ໃນທີ່ນີ້ເຮົາຈະໝາຍວ່າຜ່ານ ແລະ ກັບຄືນໄປຫາລ"
"າຍການທົດສອບຈາກເມນູດ້ານເທິງ"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt your\n"
"                    Odoo setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານໄດ້ສຳເລັດການທົດລອງໃຊ້ຕົວຢ່າງແລ້ວ! ຍັງມີອີກຫຼາຍວິທີໃນການປັບແຕ່ງ\n"
"                    Odoo ໃຫ້ເໝາະສົມກັບຄວາມຕ້ອງການຂອງທຸລະກິດຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries &gt;\n"
"                    Upgrade your package and check the related box"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ນຳເຂົ້າຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງບໍ? ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້ ໂດຍໄປທີ່ Apps &gt; Industries &gt;\n"
"                    Upgrade your package ແລະ ໝາຍເອົາຫ້ອງທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You now have a new recipe as BOM which will be used for the structured &amp;"
" bold assemblage!"
msgstr ""
"ຕອນນີ້ທ່ານມີສູດໃໝ່ໃນ BOM ເຊິ່ງຈະຖືກນຳໃຊ້ສຳລັບການປະສົມແບບ structured &amp; bold!"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid "You now have available malbec must for some assemblages!"
msgstr "ຕອນນີ້ທ່ານມີນ້ຳໝາກອະງຸ່ນ malbec ທີ່ພ້ອມສຳລັບການປະສົມແລ້ວ!"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You should be able to execute the following flows to have an overview of various flows\n"
"            you can quickly execute with this package using Odoo."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດທົດລອງເຮັດຕາມຂັ້ນຕອນຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ເພື່ອເບິ່ງພາບລວມຂອງຂະບວນການຕ່າງໆ\n"
"            ທີ່ທ່ານສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້ຢ່າງວ່ອງໄວດ້ວຍແພັກເກັດນີ້ໃນ Odoo."

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.ir_ui_view_3070
msgid ""
"Your Dynamic Snippet will be displayed here... This message is displayed "
"because you did not provide both a filter and a template to use.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"Dynamic Snippet ຂອງທ່ານຈະສະແດງຢູ່ນີ້... ຂໍ້ຄວາມນີ້ສະແດງຂຶ້ນເນື່ອງຈາກທ່ານບໍ່ໄດ້ກຳນົດທັງຕົວຕອງ "
"(filter) ແລະ ຮູບແບບ (template) ທີ່ຈະໃຊ້.<br/>"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.ir_ui_view_4048
msgid ""
"Your visit ends with a <strong>guided tasting</strong> of our signature "
"creations, including the bold <strong>Bordoo Grand Cru</strong>, the vibrant"
" <strong>Odoomatic Spice</strong>, and the elegant <strong>Pinodoo "
"Noir</strong>. Each sip tells a story of passion, craftsmanship, and the "
"unique terroir that defines our vineyard."
msgstr ""
"ການຢ້ຽມຊົມຂອງທ່ານຈະຈົບລົງດ້ວຍ <strong>ການຊິມເຫຼົ້າອະງຸ່ນ</strong> ທີ່ເປັນເອກະລັກຂອງພວກເຮົາ, ລວ"
"ມທັງ <strong>Bordoo Grand Cru</strong> ທີ່ເຂັ້ມຂຸ້ນ, <strong>Odoomatic Spice</"
"strong> ທີ່ມີຊີວິດຊີວາ, ແລະ <strong>Pinodoo Noir</strong> ທີ່ສະຫງ່າງາມ. ແຕ່ລະຢອດບົ່ງບອກເຖິ"
"ງເລື່ອງລາວຂອງຄວາມຮັກ, ຝີມື, ແລະ ຄວາມພິເສດຂອງທຳມະຊາດທີ່ສ້າງສັນສວນອະງຸ່ນຂອງພວກເຮົາ."

